refsect1.para:
Mandatory arguments to long options are also mandatory to short options.


    &opt_h;
    &opt_help;



        Display help message and terminate.





    &opt_version;



        Display version information and terminate.





    &opt_q;
    &opt_quiet;



        Do not display warning messages.





    &opt_v;
    &opt_verbose;



        Display concise intermediate messages.





    &opt_l;
    &opt_lpe;=&file;



        Name the state parameters according to the names in the LPE in &file;. This should be the LPE from which the SVC file  was generated. If this option is not used, state parameters are assigned an arbitrary name by &svc2fsm;.
